data.description: Welcome to a captivating 3-bedroom, 3.5-bathroom home in the scenic beauty of Lake Arrowhead, CA, where tranquility meets modern living. This residence boasts 1,728 square feet of living space on an expansive 18,420 square foot lot, providing a perfect blend of comfort and outdoor serenity. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a home in amazing condition, meticulously cared for and move-in ready. The thoughtful design and impeccable upkeep ensure a seamless transition into a comfortable and stylish living environment. The heart of the home is the open and inviting living space, offering breathtaking views that extend beyond the windows. This property provides a short distance to the lake, complete with lake rights, allowing you to enjoy the beauty of Lake Arrowhead at your leisure. The three bedrooms, each accompanied by its own en-suite bathroom, provide a private and cozy retreat. The additional half bath adds convenience for guests. The entire residence is bathed in natural light, creating an airy and welcoming atmosphere. One of the highlights of this property is the attached 2-car garage, offering both convenience and additional storage space. Whether you're a weekend warrior enjoying the nearby outdoor activities or a full-time resident appreciating the year-round beauty, this garage is a valuable asset. Come fall in love with this weekend getaway home or your forever home. Property address to get to the front door is as follows: 1226 Portillo LN. Lake Arrowhead, CA.
